Description:
Great Home in Old Drysdale
Set in a leafy street amongst established homes and walking distance to the shopping centre and local schools. This home was built in the days when homes were meant to last and your local builder took pride in the quality product he produced. Comprising a lovely light-filled lounge area which looks out to a private front garden. There is an adjoining second living/dining area and room in the kitchen to cook up a storm. The kitchen is older in style but well maintained with as new Fisher and Paykel appliances and a Miele dishwasher, walk-in pantry and plenty of bench space.
Polished timber floors are a highlight and flow through the three generous bedrooms all with ample storage space. There are ceiling fans to all bedrooms and a substantial reverse cycle unit which services all the interior. The bathroom is spacious and well-maintained and the ensuite partly renovated.
Behind the remote garage door the outdoor undercover area is to die for and runs the entire length of the home with ample parking for six cars or a boat, two cars and the family gatherings. The back yard is neat and tidy with plenty of space for the gardener of the family. This property sits in a sought after location and will be ready for inspection at any time.
Rhonda Humpage : 0457 313 609

Description:
RURAL BLISS ON APP. 3.4 ACRES, CLOSE TO TOWN AS WELL, THE BEST OF BOTH HERE!
A fully renovated home with sweeping rural views and everything on offer to make this home that special place for the future. Formal lounge and dining, second living with well-designed kitchen and meals, third living area (could be two rooms) is extra-large with theatre space, rumpus and large bar ... great entertainer as this all opens up to the huge undercover patio with hot tub, BBQ, plenty of extensive lighting outside for night time parties, four bedrooms, master with WIR and ensuite, others have BIR's, plus large study. 2 more bathrooms, another outside patio from the kitchen/meals as well adjacent to this a cubby house and swings, just for the children. Features include 2 wood heaters, 2 split systems, dishwasher, pantry, wall oven, gas hotplates, 8 fans, extensive storage, surround sound, biocycle treatment plant with watering system, water feature, grapevines (irrigated), electric fences, horses shelters and so much more. Double freestanding garage, with large lean to plus shed, extra space for excess vehicles/caravan, access to drive through and the landscaped gardens consist of nine fruit trees, vegetable patch, banana trees and chook pen, garden to table. This haven is on the doorstep to the wineries, brewery, beaches and loads of culinary delights.... a lifestyle choice with the lot.

Double garage plus separate double garage/workshop and cemented side drive to backyard. This is a great home, please ring for an inspection.

Description:
Perfect Lifestyle Block
Ten acres close to the Drysdale township perfect for that country lifestyle. The vendors have planted extensive shelter belts to enhance the ambiance of the property. Blocks of this nature are a rare find in this location. The three bedroom cottage and detached office-family room are ripe for renovation beckoning a freshen up to your personal taste. The current vendors have lovingly tended this property for the past thirty-five years running a successful business and raising their family.
The acreage has extensive older shedding, town water and power. Divided into several paddocks with a substantial dam. This is a block with massive potential for the future. Contact the agent for inspections.

Description:
Modern living
A beautiful home offering the best in living, outdoor entertainment & location. High vaulted ceilings are a feature in the open plan kitchen, dining & living areas. Rendered feature fence, established bushes, stunning timber walk way steps to welcome guests & providing privacy from the street.
Modern kitchen of the best quality with Caesar stone bench tops, large preparation island, feature cupboards, pot draws with soft closers. A large five burner gas cook top & 900mm oven for those aspiring chefs.
The second living room features a gas log fire place, full length feature hearth & floating display shelves.
Kingsize master bedroom with walk in robe & spacious ensuite.
Sliding glass doors lead out to the timber deck outdoor living area.
Well established gardens are a feature & a delight to meander around.
Double garage with internal access.
Located within easy walking distance to the town centre, local schools & sporting grounds.
